{"tid":547510,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【唔驚cut唔到】有線推$168體育通行證 毋須合約睇足半年","createTime":"2018-02-01T13:31:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-11T13:22:14.000Z","uid":48093,"like":4,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"9864ab9c652aa2aa483d5aa8698355208ea8a945","tid":547510,"uid":48093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T13:31:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180201/large/1517485588_69c8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180201%2Flarge%2F1517485588_69c8.jpg&h=0e682a64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n想自由自在冇合約束縛咁睇波，家陣可以了。有線電視推出「168有線體育通行證」，一次過畀168蚊，就可以任睇有線電視嘅體育節目6個月，唔使簽約。直播節目包括東南亞籃球聯賽（ABL）同BWF羽毛球巡迴賽，可以支持香港運動員，仲有獨家直播嘅歐聯，同埋德甲、FIVB排球聯賽等世界級賽事。鍾意賽馬運動嘅仲有「18台」提供嘅賽馬資訊。"},{"pid":"06173035549c0c239da046e25f5026c1e3617b49","tid":547510,"uid":143646,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T01:57:46.000Z","msg":"其實者係點 6個月total168, 定168*6?"},{"pid":"ce6d9d9890e6ae9c014a14b65c4b38157946db90","tid":547510,"uid":1441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06173035549c0c239da046e25f5026c1e3617b49","tid":547510,"uid":143646,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T01:57:46.000Z","msg":"其實者係點 6個月total168, 定168*6?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T02:09:01.000Z","msg":"應該係前者"},{"pid":"3cbf87d4f2769e373f7451bd36c21ee430328cb2","tid":547510,"uid":46042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T02:49:50.000Z","msg":"得德甲不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee69ed25e7bb47ba14a3ad48a7f8e3876885491a","tid":547510,"uid":59639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce6d9d9890e6ae9c014a14b65c4b38157946db90","tid":547510,"uid":1441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06173035549c0c239da046e25f5026c1e3617b49","tid":547510,"uid":143646,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T0