咗個remote出嚟當銀包，我果刻真係唔能知可以講乜好，成間酒樓好似靜晒，d茶客仲以為我想轉台&hellip;..就係咁我一手揸住個remote，一手揸住個銀包埋單&hellip;&hellip;..丫&hellip;&hellip;果條酒樓亞姐重能好意思問9我個搖控係咪佢地，我面都紅能埋同佢講我袋入面仲有舊解碼器連插蘇你要唔要呀。"},{"pid":"4595bb756eb9e0e8e45f97f0a520560772e810dc","tid":547510,"uid":15724,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T04:04:11.000Z","msg":"係咪可以唔裝盒？ 係既我申請嫁啦"},{"pid":"f40121db90ceaa5d66308a1c67156157e3b40484","tid":547510,"uid":16336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T22:42:02.000Z","msg":"有無人用完有包膠？"},{"pid":"91a65db9f6c88734e83086d516ab081672a239cd","tid":547510,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e8dd036ba9381b38e1cdfae4ffa5f4c5faadd40","tid":547510,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T06:42:34.000Z","msg":"唔還盒當你繼續睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T00:02:10.000Z","msg":"根本就cut唔撚到"},{"pid":"4c089642d9a09cf6cf863d0059450e1cb9b910e4","tid":547510,"uid":59966,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4595bb756eb9e0e8e45f97f0a520560772e810dc","tid":547510,"uid":15724,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T04:04:11.000Z","msg":"係咪可以唔裝盒？ 係既我申請嫁啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T00:05:15.000Z","msg":"係 申請完之後會有電話覆返資料 到時佢會問你裝唔裝舊野"},{"pid":"f6d79c6305b0649d59a3b7f13c8d0eb1405b19bc","tid":547510,"uid":129835,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T00:09:03.000Z","msg":"無j league <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"cc6f878f5f88db318e41ab10f4562e800b9acb94","tid":547510,"uid":54431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T00:27:10.000Z","msg":"168睇歐聯都抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb3731c61f940bb70c0a3ba39a1421513edf778a","tid":547510,"uid":36495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c089642d9a09cf6cf863d0059450e1cb9b910e4","tid":547510,"